$ PowerShell: Unix and cmd.exe like aliases

→ Windows/PowerShell defines a few default aliases that give → Linux[Linux] shell and former → Windows/cmd-exe[cmd.exe] users a warm feeling:

table { ll

  ~Alias name~ ☰ ~aliased function~
  cat ☰ Get-Content                                                                                                                                                           
  cd ☰ Set-Location                                                                                                                                                           
  chdir ☰ Set-Location                                                                                                                                                        
  clear ☰ Clear-Host                                                                                                                                                          
  clhy ☰ Clear-History                                                                                                                                                        
  copy ☰ Copy-Item                                                                                                                                                            
  cp ☰ Copy-Item                                                                                                                                                              
  del ☰ Remove-Item                                                                                                                                                           
  diff ☰ Compare-Object                                                                                                                                                       
  dir ☰ Get-ChildItem                                                                                                                                                         
  dnsn ☰ Disconnect-PSSession                                                                                                                                                 
  echo ☰ Write-Output                                                                                                                                                         
  erase ☰ Remove-Item                                                                                                                                                         
  foreach ☰ ForEach-Object                                                                                                                                                    
  h ☰ Get-History                                                                                                                                                             
  history ☰ Get-History                                                                                                                                                       
  kill ☰ Stop-Process                                                                                                                                                         
  ls ☰ Get-ChildItem                                                                                                                                                          
  man ☰ help                                                                                                                                                                  
  md ☰ mkdir                                                                                                                                                                  
  mount ☰ New-PSDrive                                                                                                                                                         
  move ☰ Move-Item                                                                                                                                                            
  mv ☰ Move-Item                                                                                                                                                              
  popd ☰ Pop-Location                                                                                                                                                         
  ps ☰ Get-Process                                                                                                                                                            
  pushd ☰ Push-Location                                                                                                                                                       
  pwd ☰ Get-Location                                                                                                                                                          
  rm ☰ Remove-Item                                                                                                                                                            
  rmdir ☰ Remove-Item                                                                                                                                                         
  set ☰ Set-Variable                                                                                                                                                          
  sleep ☰ Start-Sleep                                                                                                                                                         
  sort ☰ Sort-Object                                                                                                                                                          
  tee ☰ Tee-Object                                                                                                                                                            
  type ☰ Get-Content                                                                                                                                                          
  where ☰ Where-Object                                                                                                                                                        
  write ☰ Write-Output                                                                                                                                                        

table }
